485
00:43:44,530 --> 00:43:47,130
I knew that was only a dream.

486
00:43:47,430 --> 00:43:50,200
Mmmm... smells like squid...

487
00:43:51,900 --> 00:43:55,270
I'm dreaming of her even when I'm awake...

488
00:43:55,270 --> 00:43:57,880
I guess I fell on love with Kikunosuke!

489
00:43:58,310 --> 00:44:01,180
I'd like to smell her, at least...

490
00:44:03,280 --> 00:44:06,720
Inhale, exhale, inhale, exhale...

491
00:44:09,220 --> 00:44:11,390
I said shut the fuck up, you bastard!!

492
00:44:15,360 --> 00:44:20,470
My heart's full of pain, too much pain. I can't wait any more.

493
00:44:20,800 --> 00:44:25,700
Kikunosuke, wait for me! Why don't you marry your loving brother?

494
00:44:29,540 --> 00:44:32,640
