How did you know? I changed
my voice, I changed my body right down to my skeleton.

525
00:47:23,520 --> 00:47:26,420
I know my disguise was perfect. How...?

526
00:47:27,220 --> 00:47:35,360
Smell! Yukiko smells like beautiful flowers. You stink like a dirty feral dog.

527
00:47:35,730 --> 00:47:36,660
Die!

528
00:47:44,070 --> 00:47:51,980
I've seen this martial art before. It's the most evil in the world, the Abashiri 8 God attack!

529
00:47:52,750 --> 00:47:57,650
