530
00:47:57,650 --> 00:48:03,020
What a surprise! I didn't know Kikunosuke Abashiri was a girl.

531
00:48:03,020 --> 00:48:07,190
You're worthy of being feared. You're a natural born killer!

532
00:48:11,700 --> 00:48:14,300
Yukiko! Where's Yukiko!?

533
00:48:21,910 --> 00:48:25,340
This is the reason I can't quit this school.

534
00:48:25,340 --> 00:48:27,050
What a perk!

535
00:48:29,680 --> 00:48:36,750
Shirane, with your lousy grades! Shiratori, who tried to protect you, is now writhing in her own blood.

536
00:48:36,760 --> 00:48:41,490
She'll die believing you killed her, hating you from beyond the grave!

537
00:48:42,460 --> 00:48:46,730
You can explain once you meet her on the other side...

538
00:48:46,730 --> 00:48:50,270
but first, we have a few more things to do with you!

539
00:48:50,800 --> 00:48:51,140
Hey!

540
00:48:51,140 --> 00:48:52,800
No!

541
00:48:53,840 --> 00:48:56,340
Bad news! He's dead! Professor Biniku's been killed!

542
00:48:56,340 --> 00:48:57,010
What the hell?

543
00:48:58,310 --> 00:49:01,780
