552
00:49:41,020 --> 00:49:44,360
but I don't know about a mass attack.

553
00:49:48,330 --> 00:49:54,430
That's it, collect an army! They're students but they've learned the techniques of killing.

554
00:49:55,230 --> 00:49:57,400
With an army, we can win.

555
00:50:00,440 --> 00:50:05,110
Please. If we all fight together, we can defeat a group of less than 30 teachers.

556
00:50:05,610 --> 00:50:10,750
You're full of it! You beat a teacher, but just one. Don't get too full of yourself.

557
00:50:11,450 --> 00:50:13,220
Give up and go back to your room.

558
00:50:13,220 --> 00:50:16,620
Women should just quiver in fear in a corner.

559
00:50:17,460 --> 00:50:20,120
And I'm a woman, huh? Well I say you're male piece of crap.

560
00:50:20,660 --> 00:50:23,860
Anyone who hasn't got the guts to help their companions is nothing but shit!

561
00:50:24,500 --> 00:50:25,430
What did you say?

562
00:50:25,800 --> 00:50:29,570
Bitch! What gives you the right to talk to us like that?

563
00:50:29,570 --> 00:50:33,100
Wait! Wait a second. While we're wasting time like this, Yuki will be...

564
00:50:41,850 --> 00:50:47,220
It's not that we don't like doing things like this... Are you ready?

565
00:50:47,550 --> 00:50:48,720
Wait!

566
00:50:52,320 --> 00:50:57,430
One, two, one, two, I'll surprise her while she's asleep!

567
00:50:57,430 --> 00:50:59,600
How does Kikunosuke sleep?

568
00:51:00,270 --> 00:51:03,400
She's very masculine, so only in underpants?

569
00:51:03,840 --> 00:51:09,670
No, kikunosuke is fearless, so maybe naked?

570
00:51:09,680 --> 00:51:12,640
Maybe she'll be lonely, sleeping alone...

571
00:51:12,650 --> 00:51:18,680
so maybe she'll reach down and learn the joys of being a woman.

572
00:51:19,350 --> 00:51:22,750
Your brother won't let you do that!

573
00:51:24,860 --> 00:51:25,520
What?

574
00:51:26,790 --> 00:51:33,530
Leader, I'm sorry. The honor of the first taste should be for you.

575
00:51:33,570 --> 00:51:34,830
Idiot!

576
00:51:35,800 --> 00:51:37,600
Stop playing with her!

577
00:51:38,040 --> 00:51:42,940
If you have time for stupid games, use it to listen to her.

578
00:51:43,880 --> 00:51:46,640
Are you joining me?

579
00:51:47,050 --> 00:51:51,950
You'd better stop acting like a man. It's not proper for a girl.

580
00:51:53,620 --> 00:51:56,320
Hey, everyone, it's time.

581
00:51:56,720 --> 00:52:00,460
Like she said, we don't have to obey the teachers forever.

582
00:52:00,560 --> 00:52:05,500
Tell all the students! Collect weapons! We'll fight together, all of us!

583
00:52:05,830 --> 00:52:09,770
We'll rise together against this school at sunrise.

584
00:52:12,810 --> 00:52:17,510
I understand that she's dangerous, therefore I approve of her elimination.

585
00:52:17,510 --> 00:52:18,710
Yes, Principal.

586
00:52:19,150 --> 00:52:21,810
Still, what a pity...

587
00:52:21,810 --> 00:52:23,720
Yes, sir. She's pitiful.

588
00:52:23,720 --> 00:52:25,380
Idiot!

589
00:52:28,890 --> 00:52:31,390
I dind't mean that Abashiri was pitiful.

590
00:52:31,390 --> 00:52:36,060
I said that all of you are pathetic, scared of a child.

591
00:52:39,470 --> 00:52:43,870
Riot! The students are rioting and Abashiri's in charge!

592
00:52:43,870 --> 00:52:45,570
What the hell?!

593
00:52:47,070 --> 00:52:53,900
<i>The price of betrayal</i>

594
00:53:11,240 --> 00:53:17,940
We can win now!! Now it's our turn to let them taste the fear of death.

595
00:53:21,380 --> 00:53:23,780
We can get new students.

596
00:53:24,250 --> 00:53:29,120
I can't let these live after they've disobeyed the teachers of Paradice High.

597
00:53:30,420 --> 00:53:32,160
Kill them all.

598
00:53:39,530 --> 00:53:43,470
[ We're waiting for you a the old school building. Let's see how much power you have. ]

599
00:53:43,770 --> 00:53:47,970
Shit, too late! They've escaped into the ruins out back.

600
00:53:48,440 --> 00:53:50,910
Boys! Wake up, wake up!!

601
00:53:50,910 --> 00:53:52,480
Wake the fuck up!!

602
00:53:52,480 --> 00:53:54,350
What did you do, father, you bastard!

603
00:53:54,450 --> 00:53:58,820
Nao! I..I think I had Kikunosuke enter the most insane school I've ever heard of!

604
00:53:58,820 --> 00:54:02,120
Where's Kichiza? Where's Goemon? Why aren't they here?

605
00:54:02,120 --> 00:54:04,590
My sense of premonition has never failed.

606
00:54:04,590 --> 00:54:07,490
Something horrible will happen at the Paradice School.

607
00:54:07,490 --> 00:54:09,730
Kikunosuke's in danger!

608
00:54:12,300 --> 00:54:15,600
We can't undo what we've done, now that we've come this far.

609
00:54:16,100 --> 00:54:18,100
Well, what'll we do?

610
00:54:18,410 --> 00:54:19,810
The line is too long.

611
00:54:20,170 --> 00:54:26,780
We'll separate into small groups. Girls supporting the others, each group fighting individually. Am I clear?

612
00:54:26,780 --> 00:54:27,880
Yes!!

613
00:54:29,350 --> 00:54:33,790
You're a great commander, for a girl! You're not just a girl, are you?

614
00:54:36,090 --> 00:54:37,120
Let's go!

615
00:54:41,490 --> 00:54:47,500
I can climb this wall, no problems. Can't be a great pervert, otherwise.

616
00:54:47,500 --> 00:54:48,600
Here!

617
00:54:49,170 --> 00:54:51,740
Wow! Great!!

618
00:54:51,740 --> 00:54:54,970
I'm glad I came all this way.

619
00:54:57,440 --> 00:54:58,140
Who are you?

620
00:54:58,650 --> 00:55:00,710
Just a pervert.

621
00:55:00,980 --> 00:55:03,720
Please Mr. Pervert, hurry up and help me...

622
00:55:03,720 --> 00:55:07,650
I can't do that. This is a special chance for me.

623
00:55:09,760 --> 00:55:13,190
Hurry. Please, or Kikunosuke will be...

624
00:55:13,190 --> 00:55:15,160
What? Kikunosuke?

625
00:55:15,160 --> 00:55:18,560
Who are you? How did you get in here?

626
00:55:18,570 --> 00:55:21,070
I thought today was the day for the PTA to visit.

627
00:55:21,070 --> 00:55:23,470
I'm a brother of Miss Abashiri and would like to see her class...

628
00:55:23,700 --> 00:55:25,970
What? You're Abashiri's brother?

629
00:55:25,970 --> 00:55:30,810
Well then, I'll let you watch Kikunosuke's execution to your heart's content.

630
00:55:30,810 --> 00:55:31,580
What?

631
00:55:34,450 --> 00:55:35,550
What's wrong?

632
00:55:35,550 --> 00:55:38,250
Nothing. Now we've got more bait for the trap.

633
00:55:39,290 --> 00:55:42,090
This is group 2. We haven't come across the enemy.

634
00:55:42,090 --> 00:55:44,060
We're heading to point #2.

635
00:55:47,390 --> 00:55:48,530
The enemy!!

636
00:55:48,760 --> 00:55:51,760
I've been waiting for you kids. Welcome to hell.

637
00:55:58,200 --> 00:56:01,510
Do you really think students can win against teachers?

638
00:56:05,610 --> 00:56:08,080
It's strated! Everybody's going to be killed...

639
00:56:08,080 --> 00:56:09,580
Shhh! Don't make any noise!

640
00:56:10,880 --> 00:56:12,320
Something sneaking up on us, but I can't see it...

641
00:56:13,090 --> 00:56:13,790
Where is it?

642
00:56:18,490 --> 00:56:19,690
I don't want to die!

643
00:56:19,860 --> 00:56:20,830
Don't get separated from us!

644
00:56:31,100 --> 00:56:34,810
You're a pretty good fighter, the rumors were right.

645
00:56:35,580 --> 00:56:39,850
I'm "Mademoiselle Honey". Everybody at Paradice High calls me that.

646
00:56:39,950 --> 00:56:42,850
I didn't know there were female teachers in this school.

647
00:56:43,220 --> 00:56:45,220
Answer me. Where's Yuki?

648
00:56:45,490 --> 00:56:50,920
Don't worry. She's around here somewhere, along with another lure.

649
00:56:50,920 --> 00:56:55,690
But I guess that's not really necessary, since you're going to die right here.

650
00:56:56,630 --> 00:56:57,200
From where...

651
00:56:59,070 --> 00:56:59,630
What speed!

652
00:57:01,570 --> 00:57:04,540
Are you a master of the Abashiri 8 God martial arts?

653
00:57:04,540 --> 00:57:06,340
You don't look tough enough.

654
00:57:07,610 --> 00:57:09,710
The wounds from yesterday are still painful...

655
00:57:11,340 --> 00:57:13,380
