656
00:57:13,380 --> 00:57:17,850
This is the smell of sweet honey, which makes girls more girlish.

657
00:57:18,050 --> 00:57:20,250
You'll soon see its effects.

658
00:57:21,450 --> 00:57:24,360
How are you feeling? Don't you feel something mysterious?

659
00:57:24,360 --> 00:57:30,430
Sweet, painful and more... I'll guide you to the pleasures of being a woman!

660
00:57:31,700 --> 00:57:35,570
Well, well, you've become so sensitive...

661
00:57:35,570 --> 00:57:38,870
Don't you have any inclination to masochism?

662
00:57:42,880 --> 00:57:44,110
Escaping me is futile!

663
00:57:46,910 --> 00:57:52,550
Bloodlust has eneveloped this whole school. I can hear faint screaming...

664
00:57:52,550 --> 00:57:56,760
