665
00:57:56,860 --> 00:57:57,990
Looks like it.

666
00:57:58,020 --> 00:58:00,860
Kikunosuke is the most important person in the Abashiri Family.

667
00:58:01,430 --> 00:58:02,960
I won't let her die!!

668
00:58:04,200 --> 00:58:08,470
You can't get away from me. Do you know why I'm called Honey?

669
00:58:08,530 --> 00:58:09,530
