670
00:58:10,840 --> 00:58:12,970
What sweet honey invites instant death?

671
00:58:12,970 --> 00:58:15,310
What is the taste of this solution, which dissolves all?

672
00:58:19,080 --> 00:58:21,150
Dissolve into nothingness!!

673
00:58:23,050 --> 00:58:25,250
You can take your clothes off one piece at a time, just like that.

674
00:58:26,290 --> 00:58:29,250
The game is over. Now, you die.

675
00:58:29,790 --> 00:58:31,020
I've got to get closer to her to win!

676
00:58:40,200 --> 00:58:44,040
I don't like to brag, but I'e got the best footwork in Paradice High.

677
00:58:44,040 --> 00:58:45,840
You can't win.

678
00:58:46,240 --> 00:58:47,040
Prepare yourself!

679
00:58:49,140 --> 00:58:50,040
Die!

680
00:58:59,190 --> 00:59:02,120
Honey! My honey, on my face!!

681
00:59:03,520 --> 00:59:04,560
My face!

682
00:59:09,460 --> 00:59:13,630
I can't believe it took so long to finish off just one teacher...

683
00:59:19,840 --> 00:59:21,410
What's the matter? Come on, attack me.

684
00:59:21,410 --> 00:59:23,380
That's what you came here for, right?

685
00:59:23,380 --> 00:59:26,580
I'm scared! Mother!!

686
00:59:28,980 --> 00:59:29,920
Mother...

687
00:59:35,590 --> 00:59:39,690
Here you are, Mister Leader! You'd better surrender to protect yourself.

688
00:59:39,690 --> 00:59:42,990
You've only half as many students as you started with.

689
00:59:43,100 --> 00:59:47,400
I don't care. Students can be replaced.

690
00:59:50,440 --> 00:59:51,640
Who are you?

691
00:59:52,110 --> 00:59:55,840
I've cultivated these forces in secret. These seven are mine alone.

692
00:59:58,540 --> 00:59:59,710
Uh.. my glasses.

693
