695
01:00:11,020 --> 01:00:11,690
Leader!

696
01:00:14,090 --> 01:00:17,830
You're the cruelest of all teh teachers.

697
01:00:18,100 --> 01:00:21,530
You laughed strangely every time you killed a student.

698
01:00:22,570 --> 01:00:24,870
