700
01:00:30,980 --> 01:00:32,680
You asshole!

701
01:00:33,310 --> 01:00:39,320
Besides that, they are nothing. If we kill the Principal, they'll betray the school and join our side immediately.

702
01:00:48,560 --> 01:00:52,400
I guess tehre are a lot of people who want to die in this school.

703
01:00:53,200 --> 01:00:57,240
