704
01:00:57,240 --> 01:01:00,140
no matter what your technique! He's Daemon Abashiri!

705
01:01:01,710 --> 01:01:03,170
Daemon Abashiri!!

706
01:01:03,640 --> 01:01:07,910
I could never forget that voice. Danjuro Namakubi, right?

707
01:01:07,910 --> 01:01:08,850
Yes, it is I.

708
01:01:09,280 --> 01:01:11,480
This is the third time we've fought, isn't it?

709
01:01:11,950 --> 01:01:13,920
And there shall not be a fourth.

710
01:01:14,450 --> 01:01:18,290
What bullshit! Stop babbling, old man!

711
01:01:18,690 --> 01:01:21,930
Stop, Nao! You're no match for that one!

712
01:01:29,900 --> 01:01:31,040
What the hell is this?

713
01:01:32,840 --> 01:01:34,810
My body's becoming numb.

714
01:01:37,980 --> 01:01:39,310
Naojiro!

715
01:01:46,190 --> 01:01:50,990
I found out that the Abashiri Family did this. Just two of them did all this!

716
01:01:50,990 --> 01:01:53,460
They're too strong... like monsters!

717
01:01:53,830 --> 01:01:55,930
But why are the Abashiris here?

718
01:01:56,260 --> 01:01:58,630
It's Kikunosuke, the one we knew as Shiratori!

719
01:01:58,630 --> 01:02:00,530
She's the Abashiri's daughter.

720
01:02:01,070 --> 01:02:05,670
Then, we'll have to fight the Abashiri Family too.

721
01:02:06,510 --> 01:02:09,040
They're worse than the teachers.

722
01:02:09,040 --> 01:02:12,940
Don't worry. I found some good hostages for the battle.

723
01:02:13,180 --> 01:02:16,920
I see. There's no better way to use them.

724
01:02:17,850 --> 01:02:21,220
It's strange. I haven't seen any teachers for a while.

725
01:02:22,020 --> 01:02:23,590
It's too quiet...

726
01:02:25,320 --> 01:02:28,290
Hold it, Kikunosuke! It's not necessary to fight any longer.

727
01:02:29,160 --> 01:02:30,260
How the hell do you know that name?

728
01:02:30,630 --> 01:02:35,700
Your family came and helped us. The outcome of the battle has been decided.

